				<td colspan="2"><span>Personally, I have messages hotkeyed for lull, mez and charm.  The first tells people what there is that I'm NOT pulling, the second reminds them that they're supposed to be assisting the main tank, and the third simply says, &quot;Hey, look at me, I just doubled my DPS and halved the damage we're taking!&quot; <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
On an added note, as I've seen elsewhere it's a good idea to make full use of %o, %s and %t in your messages to your group, so that they can distinguish between two mobs with the same name but different genders.
<br />

<br />
